title: Strawberry Streusel Cake Recipe Demonstration - Joyofbaking.com
description:
Recipe here: http://www.joyofbaking.com/cakes/StrawberryStreuselCake.html Stephanie Jaworski of Joyofbaking.com demonstrates how to make a Strawberry Streusel Cake. While I call this a Strawberry Streusel Cake, you could also call it a Strawberry Buckle. I really like this type of dessert. It's a Coffee Cake (Kuchen) of sorts, with three delicious layers. On the bottom is a soft and fluffy white butter cake, followed by a layer of fresh strawberries, then it's finished with a crunchy Graham Cracker Crumb Streusel.
